-----
view


join files togeter using cat commands


$cat file1.txt file2.txt file3.txt file4.txt 
hello 
there
you
beautiful



$ cat file[1-5].txt > beautiful.txt
$ cat beautiful.txt 
hello 
there
you
beautiful


$ cat file[1-4].txt | tac
beautiful
you
there
hello 

reverse files vertically using tac command
tac beautiful.txt 
beautiful
you
there
hello 

reverse files horizontally using rev command
$ rev beautiful.txt 
 olleh
ereht
uoy
lufituaeb

use head tail to cut out just what you want

===============
sort data
sort files and data using sort commands

you can sort tabular data using -k option

ls -lh /etc | head -n 20 | sort -k 6M
total 1.1M
-rw-r--r--.  1 root root      1 Jan 30  2023 at.deny
